These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, poppy, daisy
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, cat, fish
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, 7up
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, magic-tricks, filmmaking
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving and the owner of the cat have different parity positions##9
 2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not the person who growspoppy##6
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the owner of the rabbit and the person who growspoppy have different parity positions##9
 6. the owner of the fish is the person who growsdaisy##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 9. the owner of the cat and the person who growsdaisy have different parity positions##9
10. the person drinking iced-tea is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Job           | tulip | poppy | daisy    |
| Music-Genre   | rabbit       | cat   | fish   |
| Nationality   | juice    | iced-tea | 7up  |
| Transport     | filmmaking   | magic-tricks       | skydiving |

