.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, game, swisher
City: berlin, paris, venice
3 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, domino
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, tower
1. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the right of the swisher-smoker##5
2. the townhouse house is not to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##8
3. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5
4. the person playing scrabble and the game-smoker have the same parity positions##9
5. the person traveling to berlin and the ritmeester-smoker have different parity positions##9
6. the person traveling to venice is in the middle##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
8. the person playing domino is the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3     |
| Food          | swisher  | ritmeester         | game |
| Hobby         | berlin | venice | paris   |
| Movie-Genre   | snooker     | domino       | scrabble     |
| Transport     | townhouse       | gothic-revival          | tower    |

