.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-3::.
House: gothic-revival, craftsman, colonial
3 different pets are kept: horse, hedgehog, rabbit
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, polish, american
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, october, march
1. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the colonial house##8
2. the polish is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
3. the colonial house is the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
5. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
6. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the polish##8
8. the gothic-revival house and the american have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | gothic-revival | craftsman | colonial |
| Movie-Genre   | rabbit      | horse   | hedgehog  |
| Music-Genre   | american        | russian  | polish         |
| Transport     | march       | april    | october       |

