1. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
2. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the left of the person eating spinach##5
3. the person playing poker and the person who growsaconite have different parity positions##9
4. the person playing snooker is in the middle##1
5. the person who likes red is on the far right##1
6. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
7. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
8. the person playing snooker is not to the right of the person who growsdaffodil##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |       3       |
| Job           | tulip    | aconite | daffodil |
| Movie-Genre   | poker | snooker       | canasta     |
| Pet           | fuchsia        | aquamarine      | red          |
| Transport     | blueberry        | pomegranate         | spinach     |

