3 different games are played: poker, whist, snooker
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, climbing
1. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5
2. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the prince-smoker##5
3. the person who's sport is climbing is between the vegafina-smoker and the person who's sport is baseball##2
4. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
5. the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's sport is surfing have the same parity positions##9
6. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
7. the prince-smoker is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
8. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
9. the person playing snooker is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |
| Hobby         | february  | august   | december |
| Job           | prince   | chaman | vegafina |
| Movie-Genre   | snooker   | whist  | poker     |
| Nationality   | baseball | climbing    | surfing  |

